== 民調列表 ==
由於[[北爱尔兰|北愛爾蘭]]的政治分野以[[愛爾蘭聯合主義|聯合主義]]對[[愛爾蘭民族主義|民族主義]]和[[愛爾蘭共和主義|共和主義]]主導，而政黨和政治版圖均異於[[大不列顛島|大不列顛]]；另一方面，[[直布罗陀|直布羅陀]]擁有自己的[[直布罗陀议会|議會]]和政黨，亦不是[[英國選舉|英國國會大選]]的選區，因此兩地通常都不被納入民調範圍<ref name="NI">{{cite web |url=http://ukpollingreport.co.uk/blog/archives/9540 |title=Northern Irish poll on the EU referendum |publisher=ukpollingreport.co.uk |date=2015-11-06 |accessdate=2015-11-11 |archive-date=2019-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331143115/http://ukpollingreport.co.uk/blog/archives/9540 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

下表中的大部分民調調查機構都是{{tsl|en|British Polling Council|英國民意調查理事會}}的成員，全數公開他們的調查數據、調查方法和民調委託機構<ref>{{cite web|url=http://researchbriefings.files.parliament.uk/documents/LLN-2014-028/LLN-2014-028.pdf|title=Understanding and Sourcing Political Opinion Polls|date=2014-08-08|accessdate=2016-06-18|author=Tom Ashford|publisher=House of Lords Library|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403162136/https://researchbriefings.files.parliament.uk/documents/LLN-2014-028/LLN-2014-028.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過{{tsl|en|Qriously}}、{{tsl|en|Stan Greenberg|史丹·堅伯|堅坤羅研究中心}}、[[皮尤研究中心|皮尤研究中心]]和{{tsl|en|Michael Ashcroft|米高·艾司葛|艾司葛勳爵}}都並非理事會成員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.britishpollingcouncil.org/officers-members/|title=Officers / Members|publisher=British Polling Council|accessdate=2016-06-18|archive-date=2020-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215010938/http://www.britishpollingcouncil.org/officers-members/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因此應謹慎研究他們的民調結果<ref>{{cite web|url=https://fullfact.org/news/polls-damn-polls-and-statistics/|title=Polls, Damn Polls and Statistics|date=2015-05-06|accessdate=2016-06-18|publisher=Full Fact|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104032359/https://fullfact.org/news/polls-damn-polls-and-statistics/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

