=== 艾司葛勳爵 ===
{{tsl|en|Michael Ashcroft|米高·艾司葛|艾司葛勳爵}}訪問了20,000名英國居民，就自己有幾大可能投票脫歐或留歐而評分，結果在2015年12月公佈。最終47%受訪者會投票脫歐，38%會投票留歐，另外有14%尚未有決定<ref name="Ashcroft poll">{{cite web |url=http://lordashcroftpolls.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Europe-poll-tables-Dec-15.pdf |title=Lord Ashcroft Polls |date= |accessdate=2016-07-04 |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929204853/http://lordashcroftpolls.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Europe-poll-tables-Dec-15.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="argument">{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/eureferendum/12054892/Lord-Ashcroft-The-argument-over-whether-to-remain-or-leave-the-EU-is-only-just-beginning.html |title=Lord Ashcroft: The argument over whether to remain or leave the EU is only just beginning |work=The Daily Telegraph |date=2015-12-17 |accessdate=2015-12-19 |last=Lord Ashcroft |archive-date=2019-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331132015/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/eureferendum/12054892/Lord-Ashcroft-The-argument-over-whether-to-remain-or-leave-the-EU-is-only-just-beginning.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年初，艾司葛訪問其他歐盟成員國公民對英國脫歐的意見。沒有成員國的大多數受訪者希望英國脫歐；除塞浦路斯、捷克和斯洛文尼亞外的所有成員國大多數受訪者都希望英國留歐，尤以立陶宛的支持率最高<ref name="Ashcroft">{{cite web|title='You Should Hear What They Say About You' – what our European neighbours think of Britain and the EU|date=2016-02-17|url=http://lordashcroftpolls.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/LORD-ASHCROFT-POLLS-You-Should-Hear-What-They-Say-About-You-EU28-Poll-Report-Feb-2016.pdf|accessdate=2016-03-18|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227083042/http://lordashcroftpolls.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/LORD-ASHCROFT-POLLS-You-Should-Hear-What-They-Say-About-You-EU28-Poll-Report-Feb-2016.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

